name: Colossus Project
description:
A Colossus arise..

Deep under a mountain lives a sleeping giant, capable to eighter help humanity or create destruction...

This Checkpoint is capable to produce nearly everything.. Colossus is very good creating extremly realistic pictures, anime and art. I am working on this since months together with my twin brother.

I am constantly improving this project. Please help me with this project with your feedback. Send in reviews, pictures and feel free to leave a comment.

Version 2.03 is actually a huge deal for me. I improved Version 2.0. It's even more stable and it has the VAE baked inside. Also this one just needs around 2GB on your hard drive instead of 4GB.

Note:

This version does't need a VAE anymore..

If you want to use it in FP32 ((Full precision)) or if you want to use a custom VAE download Version 2.0 instead.

Best sampler in my opinion with Version 2.0:

Euler a, UniPc, DPM ++ 2M Karras

DPM ++2M SDE Karras, DDIM, (very good for photorealism)

Experiment with it and show me the results in the gallery.

Colossus neads some guidance regarding styles.. give it a simple style idea to work with. If the style isn't showing up try to give the style more importance. Here is a example.

((anime art:1.3))

Suprise me which styles are actually working on this thing :-)

Do not use this version with: ng_deepnegative_v1_75t ;this causes some weird issues.

If the result looks oversaturated or got outlines try to lower the cfg-scale or use the dynamic Thresholding (cfg fix). You can also experimenting with the resolution. this thing can handle even up to 1000x1000 images, however this can sometines result with errors.. feel free to experiment with this as well

Disclaimer and Warning: This checkpoint is fully uncensored. Only your imagination is the limit. Beware of this.. It's not intented to create just porn but it can be very horny. I would advice to consider this and maybe add NSFW in negative prompts... Don't use this to harm others... Please use this responsible! You are fully responsible for your actions!
